    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This altar is a large stone hearth that is normally kept blazing and features a prominent image of Erastil wielding his sacred bow, using the holy weapon either in defense of a home or to hunt game for food. Praying at the altar grants a +2 circumstance bonus on Handle Animal and Heal checks, or one of the following magic weapon special abilities (worshiper's choice) to one magic weapon carried or wielded by the worshiper: animal-bane, conservingUE, huntsmanUE, or merciful. This effect is suppressed if the weapon leaves the worshiper's grasp, but resumes if the weapon is returned to the worshiper.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, abundant ammunitionUC, cure light wounds,  detect animals or plants, magic circle against chaos, magic circle  against evil, summon monster I, creator must worship Erastil</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Inner Sea Gods",
